Well, it was because these two locations were on the same longitude.

00:06:54.935 --> 00:07:00.555
Importantly, they were on the Paris Meridian, the French equivalent to the now more

00:07:00.595 --> 00:07:06.255
popular Greenwich Meridian, which is a straight line going directly from north to south.

00:07:07.725 --> 00:07:14.875
If you were to draw a line from the North Pole to Paris, then it would have passed through Dunkirk.

00:07:15.525 --> 00:07:20.645
