00:11:59.780 --> 00:12:06.280
It was a gargantuan effort, and every small error in the angles, every imprecise

00:12:06.280 --> 00:12:12.680
reading, would multiply over hundreds of kilometres, so they had to be meticulous.

00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:18.742
